title: Ahh, the comfortable life... Home in Tumwater. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Another beautiful new construction home by Gallardo Homes!', '2691 sf, 4 beds/2.5 baths plus upper floor bonus room and convenient upper floor utility room.', 'Open kitchen and living space with slider access to generous back yard.', 'Kitchen features quartz counter-tops with undermount sink, tons of cabinets and prep space, island w/dine-in space and stainless steel appliances.', 'Exquisite Primary Suite offers a private bath & walk-in closet.', 'Easy care LVP flooring in kitchen/1st floor hallway/bathrooms & utility room.', '3 car (tandem) garage, front landscaping with sod/bark in rear.', 'Cement fiber siding (25 yr warranty) and Architectural Roofing (limited lifetime warranty).', 'Close to shopping, dining, amenities and easy freeway access.', '***Please Text & Call', 'show contact info', 'For More Details & Pics***']
